GSD.description:
Kconfig.debug: provide a little extra FRAME_WARN leeway when KASAN is enabled

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.158 by commit f09ac62f0e3f1b4a490d9922a3ac95f554297828. For more details please see the references link.
